  renderPathForWeight(weight, color, pathsByWeight);

const Timer = forwardRef<SVGSVGElement, IconProps>((props, ref) => (
  <IconBase ref={ref} {...props} renderPath={renderPath} />
));

Timer.displayName = "Timer";

export default Timer;
